This model is mixed mainly with Hassansblend 1.2 and DeliberateV2, with many other small mixes, so it has an extremely great variety and potential.

Most prompts for photo real will work; I copied some of the prompts I see here, and they all work great. It works even better if you start the prompt with "A photo of..." since SD is trained this way.

It can do all the good stuff in hassansblend1.2 like tenticle sex and reverse cowgirl in better colors.

It makes good low light photos with Theovercomer8's Contrast Fix LORA 1.5 version. (Model works without Theovercomer8's Contrast Fix LORA; just results will be brighter.)

Also, shout out to PureErosFace_V1! This inversion can make sexy Asian faces easily!

Check out my Twitter to see all previous works using this model.

Have fun!
